# ─── AI PROVIDERS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Priority chain (top = highest priority). Uncomment what you want active.
# All keys are optional — the first key found wins; others act as fallbacks.
#
# 1. OpenAI — GPT-4o (primary) + GPT-4o-mini (fallback)
# OPENAI_API_KEY_GPT4O=sk-proj-...
# OPENAI_API_KEY_GPT4O_MINI=sk-proj-...
#
# 2. OpenRouter — Gemini (fast) + Haiku (fallback)
# OPENROUTER_KEY_GEMINI=sk-or-v1-...
# OPENROUTER_KEY_HAIKU=sk-or-v1-...
#
# 3. Direct Anthropic — Haiku (emergency)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
#
# 4. Direct Google Gemini — last resort
# GOOGLE_GENERATIVE_AI_API_KEY=AIza...
